summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting guy wire and anchor easements over portions of Tract 27, Sunnyside Five Acre Tracts; Government Lot 12, Section 4, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; Lots 8, 9, 10 and 11, Block 386, Seattle Tidelands; Lot 7, Block 1, Public Benefit Subdivision of Tract 17 Georgetown; Parcel E and Parcel F of City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 8907586; and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
